comments: McCollum (NOP) firms up in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and absorbs the marginal contact while setting the screen.
Lively II (DAL) and Nance Jr. (NOP) briefly engage and disengage as they pursue the rebound.
Williams (DAL) is already in Jones' (NOP) path when contact occurs and he does not deliver contact.
Jones (NOP) brings his forearm towards Williams' (DAL) front as they separate, and the contact is marginal.
Williams (DAL) firms up in Jones' (NOP) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Nance Jr. (NOP) establishes himself in Williams' (DAL) path and absorbs the contact during the pick.
Williams (DAL) does not maintain verticality and makes contact with Williamson's (NOP) arm that affects his driving shot attempt.
Lively II (DAL) and Nance Jr. (NOP) come together at the same spot in the air while pursuing the rebound, and the contact is marginal.
Williams (DAL) briefly grasps Nance Jr.'s (NOP) arm and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
Nance Jr. (NOP) establishes himself in Hardaway Jr.'s (DAL) path and does not deliver illegal contact when setting the pick.
Williams (DAL) firms up over his left leg in Jones' (NOP) path, and he absorbs the contact during the pick.
Kleber (DAL) commits a take foul on Williamson (NOP).
Daniels (NOP) commits a take foul on Irving (DAL).
Irving (DAL) avoids making contact with Ingram's (NOP) arm as he contests the jump shot.
Williams (DAL) turns towards Jones (NOP) with his arm slightly forward, and marginal contact occurs as they pursue the rebound.
McCollum (NOP) commits a take foul on Kleber (DAL).
